did.unittitle: Rice University Associate Provost Search records
did.abstract: These materials include correspondence, minutes, notes, and other materials related to the searches for an Associate Provost during the years 1986, 1995, and 1996. Also included are the materials submitted by the applicants for each search. This material is restricted.

bioghist.head: Historical Note
bioghist.p: Rice University's Office of the Provost oversees academic, instructional, and research-related matters.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: These materials include correspondence, minutes, notes, and other materials related to the Rice University Associate Provost searches conducted in 1986, 1995, and 1996. Some of the materials were created by the search committees in order to conduct the search in each year, while other materials, including resumes, references, and correspondence, were provided by the applicants of each year's search.
